This roll bundles the FSA, Mummer, and AMOS sequence alignment packages.  To
install, execute these instructions on a Rocks development machine (e.g., a
frontend), starting in this directory:

% make
% rocks add roll *.iso
% rocks enable roll fsa
% cd /export/rocks/install
% rocks create distro
% rocks run roll fsa | bash

In addition to the software itself, the roll installs FSA environment module
files in /opt/modulefiles/applications/beast.
